snippet.title: Triforce Johnson talks about Jamaican made indie game Black Otaku S.O.S
snippet.description:
Triforce Johnson of Empire Arcadia gives us his two cents on the Jamaican made Indie game "Black Otaku - S.O.S", created by Canadian based indie devs, Def Sauce.
